Package options

Package containing classes used for specification and processing of command line argument

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Argument<T>
    Class representing option's argument
    Argument.Builder<T>
    This class is used to create arguments
    Option
    This class represent the option
    Option.Builder
    Builder class which is used to create new options
    Parser
    This class main purpose is to parse the input and create ParsingResult object
    ParsingResult
    This class contains all related information about options after parsing is done
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ArgumentPresence
    Enum for representing whether argument is mandatory or optional for particular option
    Option.Builder.SwitchType
    Enum used to specify if the switch is short or long
